   SCI-MARIJUANA-HEART (Undated) _ In the first hour after smoking
marijuana, a middle-aged or elderly person's risk of heart attack
can shoot up nearly five-fold, according to a study that is is the
first to show such a link. By Holcomb B. Noble.
