</P>
<P>
   AT SLAIN GIRL'S SCHOOL, REASSURANCE AND QUESTIONS
</P>
<P>
   A5093 BC-EXP-PALM-IPO-NYT 396 21:52 U A
</P>
<P>
   OFFSPRING UPSTAGES A PARENT IN PALM INC.'S INITIAL TRADING
</P>
<P>
   A5080 BC-MAINE-COMPUTERS-NYT 783 21:43 U A
</P>
<P>
   GOVERNOR PROPOSES GIVING A LAPTOP COMPUTER TO EVERY 7TH-GRADER
IN MAINE
