<TEXT>
<P>
   These excellent articles are from the current ECONOMIST magazine
(week beginning 4 March 2000); they have all moved to the ``k''
commentary category code.  &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (ATTN. EDITORS: The following material from The New York Times
Syndicate is for use by clients of The Economist. Nonsubscribers
can use this article only by special arrangement. For purchase
information, call 1-888-269-8796.) &LR;  &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
