   &UR; MEXICO'S CERTIFIABLY MAD WAR ON DRUGS &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   It is known as the ``February surprise.'' Every year, shortly
before the U.S. government announces on March 1 which countries it
``certifies'' as willing allies in the war on illegal drugs, Mexico
unveils a new and bold anti-drugs initiative. This year, though,
the surprise was on Mexico. &QL;
