   PALSY _ A Fairborn girl's upcoming trip for an experimental
cerebral palsy treatment in Toronto has begun kindling some local
interest in clinically testing the procedure. Tiffany Foxx will
undergo about 100 hyperbaric oxygen treatments in June and August.
Her parents and doctors hope that breathing concentrated oxygen
