Georgia before Super Tuesday with several Atlanta appearances
Friday. The six-hour visit starts with a 4:15 pm stop at West End's
Chanterelle's restaurant, followed by 6 pm Democratic Party
reception (closed) at the downtown Hyatt, then 7:30 pm appearance
at Democrats' Jefferson-Jackson Day fundraiser at the Hyatt.
