<HEADLINE>
GAYS, STAND UP AND BE COUNTED THIS SUPER TUESDAY  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  ATTENTION EDITORS: The following material from The New York Times
Syndicate is for use by NEW AMERICA NEWS SERVICE clients.
Nonsubscribers can use this article only by special arrangement.
For purchase information, see end of text. 
 &HT;    
 By CHUCK COLBERT  
 &HT;    Gay Democrats and Republicans _ in nearly a dozen states from
Massachusetts to Ohio, Georgia to Missouri and New York to
California _ head to the polls on Super Tuesday to make their
