Rev. Jesse L. Jackson and Rubin ``Hurricane'' Carter visited the
North County Correctional Facility, where they screened ``The
Hurricane'' for inmates and discussed related criminal justice
issues, as well as delivering a motivational message. By Orith
Goldberg. (Will run in the ``a'' national and ``n'' state news
files.)
</P>
